lineage.Process:
CalculateField hru_polygon_layer RECHR_MAX rech_max_func(!SOIL_RT_MX!, !AWC!) PYTHON "def rech_max_func(soil_root_max, awc):
 if soil_root_max > 18: return 18*awc
 else: return soil_root_max*awc
"

CalculateField hru_polygon_layer SOIL_TYPE soil_type_func(!CLAY_PCT!, !SAND_PCT!) PYTHON "def soil_type_func(clay, sand):
 if sand > 50: return 1
 elif clay > 40: return 3
 else: return 2
"
CalculateField hru_polygon_layer SLOWCOEF_L slowcoef_lin(!KSAT!, !DEM_SLP_R!, 90.0) PYTHON "def slowcoef_lin(ksat, slope, cs):\n return 0.1 * ksat * 0.0864 * math.sin(slope) / cs\n"

CalculateField hru_polygon_layer SLOWCOEF_S slowcoef_sq(!KSAT!, !DEM_SLP_R!, !MOIST_MAX!, !SAND_PCT!, 90.0) PYTHON "def slowcoef_sq(ksat, slope, moist_max, sand, cs):\n return 0.9 * (ksat * 0.0864 * math.sin(slope) / (moist_max * (sand / 100) * cs))\n"
